com.socrata.builders

Class SoqlQueryBuilder

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.socrata.builders.SoqlQueryBuilder

  • public class SoqlQueryBuilder
extends Object
    A Builder class for creating SoQL Queries. Since SoqlQuery is immutable, this object is for creating the SoqlQuery objects.
